{"parse":{"title":"Giant Sunfish","pageid":157644,"wikitext":{"*":"<onlyinclude>{{{{{tpl|tooltip}}}\n|mode={{{mode|}}}\n|arg={{{arg|}}}\n|name=Giant Sunfish\n|icon=INV_Misc_Fish_03\n|stack=20\n|quality=common\n|level=55\n|effect=Use: Restores 7500 health over 30 sec. Must remain seated while eating.\n|cooldown=1 sec\n|charges=1\n|ilvl=70\n|sell={{cost|c=50}}\n}}</onlyinclude>\n\n==Source==\nThe Fish may be caught in the water surrounding the [[Isle of Quel'Danas]].\n\nThe drop rate is approximatively 45% (out of a 100 sample) in open water.\n\n== Patch Changes ==\n{{Patch 2.4.0|note=Added}}\n==External links==\n<!-- Read http://www.wowwiki.com/WoWWiki:External_links before posting your links here.\nLinks that do not conform to the rules will be DELETED.\nRepeat violations may result in a BAN.\nHave a nice day. :) -->\n{{elinks-item|35285}}\n{{Elink|link=http://www.elsanglin.com/fish/giant_sunfish.html |site=El's Extreme Anglin' |icon=elsanglin}}\n\n\n[[Category:World of Warcraft common fished items]]\n[[Category:World of Warcraft food items]]"}}}